You’ll build your project in modules, so you can test each part before integration.

Modules:
	1.	Bank Statement Parser
→ Extract data from CSV/PDF.
	2.	Data Cleaning & Categorization
→ Standardize and classify transactions.
	3.	Spending Analysis Module
→ Generate category-wise summaries and habits.
	4.	ML Prediction Module
→ Predict future spending or detect overspending trends.
	5.	Budget Optimizer
→ Create before/after budget views.
	6.	AI Recommendation Agent
→ Suggest how to meet the savings goal.
	7.	Dashboard Interface
→ Visualize everything with graphs and tables.
